fields.name: Stacey
fields.bio: Having worked in salons all over the world from Ireland to Australia, Stacey has been with us for over 3 and a half years, with over 10 years of colour and styling experience. Having completed her masters in colour for Wella she is confident in all aspects of colour. Instagram - @staceyhairstyles

fields.name: Sarah
fields.bio: Sarah has been with us for almost 3 years, with 12 years of experience. Confident in a variety of different colour techniques from balayage to all over colours. Sarah is also qualified in hair extensions.

fields.name: Christina
fields.bio: Our Salon manager Christina has been with us for over 1 and a half years, with over 11 years shop floor experience, all the way from the south of Greece to London. Confident in both womens and mens hair, with qualifications from Wahl training courses. She enjoys all aspects of cutting and is a perfectionist when it comes to blow drying and styling. Christina is also qualified in hair extensions, including micro rings, nano rings, bonded glue and tape.

fields.name: Florence
fields.bio: Qualified in Barbering NVQ Level 2 from London school of barbering and Hairdressing VTCT Level 2, Florence is new to the team with over 5 years of floor experience. Confident in mens and womens cuts. Florence is also qualified in hair extensions including, rings and tapes.

fields.name: Will
fields.bio: With an impressive 21 years experience in hairdressing, Will has been part of the team for almost 2 years. Having previously come 3rd in the Loreal Colour trophy, Will is highly trained in all aspects of colour services. He is most popular amongst clients with his balayage and attention to detail on short cuts. Specialises in  Foils, Balayage and Short cuts.

fields.name: Lorenzo
fields.bio: Our Long-term stylist Lorenzo has been with us for 13 years and has over 20 years experience on the shop floor. Lorenzo has worked in a range of different environments from backstage at London fashion week, brand campaigns to Hair shows. Having previously worked with celebrities such as Annie Lennox to Marina Diamandis he has a diverse skill set. Specialises in  Precision, texture and fashion cuts and colour.

fields.name: Farrah
fields.bio: From Dublin to Berlin to London, Farrah has worked in various locations during her 15 years of salon experience, although having only been part of pimps for 9 months she brings with her an exciting range of skills. You may have seen some of her work on tv shows such as Camelot and Vikings, and movies such as Neverland and this must be the place. Specialises in  Long hair, styling, blonde and occasion hair.

fields.name: Romina
fields.bio: From Hamburg to London, Romina has been with us for over 1 year, bringing over 9 years shop floor experience. Coming from a family of hairdressers she is 3rd generation, growing up amongst her families barber shop which has been open for over 85 years. Her qualifications include a German Masters in hairdressing and Wella Master of colour. Specialises in  Highlights, all over global colour and tint.

fields.name: Rob
fields.bio: With just over 15 years salon floor experience and 2 years at pimps and pin-ups, Rob has extensive training provided by both Sassoon and Trevor Sorbie. He is a confident hair consultant and is also one of few stylists who offer our KeraStraight treatment. Specialises in  Precision/structured/shape cuttingSpecialises in  Precision/structured/shape cutting

fields.name: Greta
fields.bio: Although one of our newest additions to the team, Greta has over 10 years shop floor experience. Straight from the fashion capital Milan to London, Greta has a versatile skill set regarding cuts, ranging from classic to modern. Specialises in  Curly Hair, Cutting and blow-drys.

fields.name: Rebecca
fields.bio: Rebecca comes to us having sold her own Salon which she owned for 5 years in her hometown Yorkshire. She has now been with us for 4 years and has a total of 17 years shop floor experience. After training with Toni and Guy she went on to work on shoots with various fashion brands for Liberties and has participated in on stage demos for Salon international. Confident in all aspects of colour,  with a Wella colour expert qualification. Specialises in  Balayage and short pixie cuts.

fields.name: Olivia
fields.bio: Having worked her way up from part of our junior team, Olivia has been working as a stylist for over 2 years. She knows the salon well and what is best for her clients through her detailed consultations ensuring both stylist and client is happy with the finished look. Confident with colour services her work really shines through balayage and crazy colours. Specialises in  Crazy Colour and Balayage

fields.name: Bec
fields.bio: Having styled hair all over the world from Australia to LA to finally settling down in London, Bec has been part of the team since 2013. With impressive achievements to accompany her years of experience, such as Lead stylist on Vogue style shows to the White House fashion institute. She is an ideal stylist for those looking for colour transformations, having won both the Aveda colour harmony award and the Davines colour award.

fields.name: Cecilia
fields.bio: Having worked in several locations all over Europe our Spanish Seorita Cecilia has been with us for over 2 years and has a staggering 20 years of experience behind her. Picking up lots of different techniques and skills along the way, allowing her to adapt to each individual clients needs. With a passion for the 40s era, she is perfect for styling all occasions.

fields.name: Root Tint to Touch Up From
Olaplex Shampoo
fields.use: N4 Shampoo repairs and protects hair from everyday stresses  including damaged hair, split ends, and frizz  by re-linking broken bonds. Leaves hair easier to manage, shinier and healthier with each use. N4 is color-safe and proven to reduce breakage and strengthen all types of hair. All hair types, especially those needing clarifying or oil control.

fields.name: Olaplex Conditioner
fields.use: Leaves hair easier to manage, shinier and healthier with each use. Protects and repairs damaged hair, split ends, and frizz by re-linking broken bonds. It is color-safe and will strengthen and leave your hair stronger than ever.

fields.name: Olaplex Bonding Oil
fields.use: Dramatically increases shine, softness, and color vibrancy. N7 minimizes flyaways and frizz, while providing UV/heat protection of up to 450F/232C. All hair types, especially for those using heat tools daily.

fields.name: Olaplex Bond Smoother
fields.use: N6 strengthens, moisturizes, and speeds up blow-dry times. Excellent for all hair types, including colored and chemically treated hair, and eliminates frizz and flyaways for up to 72 hours. All hair types. Blow dry or air-dry styling.

fields.name: Lockdown
fields.use: leave-in treatment to smooth, detangle and prepare hair for styling while greatly improving shine and manageability. aControls unruly hair and reduces frizz. adds softness and shine, helps detangle and improve manageability. Recommended for frizzy, unruly, colour-treated hair.

fields.name: Root Canal
fields.use: A volumising root lift spray that builds body and texture. Adds volume and style support at the roots, improves the manageability of hair and wearability of hair styles. pump spray packaging rather than aerosol. Recommended for all hair types, especially fine hair.

fields.name: Happy Campers
fields.use: A lightweight, daily styling treatment that moisturises, strengthens and protects, while adding style support. Dual delivery as a spray or a cream for a more concentrated effect. adds moisture, reduces frizz and helps provide protection from uv and heat damage. improves styling and reduces blow-drying time while providing slight volume and hold. Recommended for all hair types; especially weak, brittle, colour-treated hair.

fields.name: Liquid Rollers
fields.use: A light hold curl balm that enhances natural curl shape while moisturising and protecting against frizz.  lightly holds to enhance natural curl shape and pattern  adds softness and shine while helping to detangle, improve manageability and condition  seals the cuticle to prevent moisture loss, reduce frizz and provide humidity control  leaves curls defined, hydrated and touchable. Recommended for all curl types, including: wavy, curly, coily and tight textures.

fields.name: Rose Oil Shampoo
fields.use: A gentle cleanser for all hair types including coloured and chemically treated hair. Infused with Rose oil for its anti inflammatory and antibacterial properties to help promote a healthy scalp. Rose oil also has amazing moisturising effects to prevent dehydration. Packed with antioxidants , wheat amino acids and Vitamins A, C, B5, and E for further Hydration, adding moisture and shine. Great for all hair types.

fields.name: Rose Oil Conditioner
fields.use: Rose Oil Conditioner is designed for weightless moisture, softness and shine. Rose oil has the ability to deliver intense moisture and hydration. The molecules of this oil are small, allowing for a deeper level of penetration when used on the hair making it great for dry, damaged and brittle hair also great for coloured and chemically treated hair. Packed full of antioxidants, like Geraniol, that can help eliminate any impurities and protect from oxidative stress. Rose oil also strengthens hair at the root, protects against frizz and adds shine, it's antiviral and antibacterial properties keep the scalp safe from irritations and other scalp problems. Shea butter and hydrolysed silk help detangling and cuticle smoothing, leaving hair weightless, silky smooth and super shiny.

fields.name: Dirty Deeds - Wax
fields.use: Creates structured looks that remain in place. creates touchable texture and builds body. flexible hold that can be restyled with ease.  Recommended for all hair types; especially thick, coarse hair.

fields.name: Fabuloso Toning Treatment
fields.use: A platinum blonde treatment that conditions while neutralising unwanted brassy, yellow tones in colour-treated blonde and lightened hair to leave it toned, refreshed and revived with added shine.  instantly refreshes and tones to extend the life of colour-treated blonde and lightened hair  nourishing treatment softens and conditions hair  restores and maintains moisture balance to reduce frizz and give brilliant shine. Recommended for dull, dry, lightened or colour-treated blonde hair

fields.name: Shebangabang
fields.use: A styling spray with an ultra-fine mist designed to create workable, pliable texture. Creates pliable texture with separation and movement. can be used on any hair type to style wet or dry hair. mist provides even distribution to easily build styles. Recommended for all hair types.

fields.name: Haze Styling Powder
fields.use: A styling powder to add volume and texture with a matte finish. Creates volume with touchable texture. pump provides even distribution for general or targeted application. refillable pump reduces environmental impact and wastage. Recommended for all hair types; especially fine, limp hair.

fields.name: Days of Grace
fields.use: A lightweight leave-in primer to prepare hair for styling. Lightly conditions and prepares hair for styling. helps provide protection from uv and heat damage. adds softness and shine, reduces frizz, helps detangle and improve manageability. Recommended for all hair types; especially fine hair.

fields.name: Salty Dog Sea Salt Spray
fields.use: A sea-esque mist to give salty, beach-based texture with a matte finish. Creates touchable beach-based texture and body. provides natural matte finish. Recommended for all hair types.

fields.name: Crop Strutters
fields.use: a styling cream for medium, malleable hold, support and separationwith medium shine.  benefits. improves styling, definition and hold. flexible hold that can be restyled with ease. easily washes out, without leaving residue. Recommended for all hair types; especially short hair.

fields.name: Water Killer
fields.use: A two-in-one dry shampoo and styling spray that makes hair feel and smell fresh again. concept. a two-in-one dry shampoo and styling spray that makes hair feel and smell fresh again.  benefits. helps prevent damage to hair through washing and blow drying. saves time. saves water. Can be used anytime, anywhere. can also be used as a texturising styling spray. Recommended for all hair types.

fields.name: No.3 Hair Perfector
fields.use: An at home treatment that reduces breakage and visibly strengthens hair, improving its look and feel. It will restore your hair's healthy appearance and texture by repairing damage and protecting hair structure. All hair types, especially for those with visible damage.

fields.name: The Great Hydrator
fields.use: An intense hydrating treatment to moisturise, soften, reduce frizz and add shine. Deeply moisturises, adds softness and shine while helping to detangle and improve manageability. Recommended for dry, colour-treated hair.

fields.name: Shape Vixen
fields.use: A volumising lotion that adds lasting body and shape memory with a touchable finish. Adds fullness and body without weighing down hair. improves styling with lasting hold. increases slip and leaves hair feeling light. Recommended for all hair types; especially fine hair.

fields.name: Macgyver
fields.use: A multi-purpose styling mousse that can be used with or without heat to create volume, separation and texture. Adds shape memory with lasting hold for improved styling. creates volume and touchable texture.easily brushes out without leaving residue. can be used with or without heat to style and/or finish wet or dry hair. Recommended for all hair types.

fields.name: Miss Malleable
fields.use: A strong hold, flexible hairspray for styling and finishing that brushes out to an invisible finish. Creates structured looks that remain in place. flexible hold that can be restyled with ease. easily brushes out without residue. fine, dry mist dries on contact to leave a non-tacky finish. Recommended for all hair types.
